        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="note default modern"><p><span class='p green'>绿色</span>为开源APP，<span class='p yellow'>黄色</span>为闭源app，推荐自己用的一些好用的应用<br><span class='p red'>Universal</span>:通用版<br><span class='p yellow'>arm64-v8a</span>:arm处理器64位<br><span class='p green'>armeabi-v7a</span>:arm处理器32位<br><span class='p cyan'>x86</span>:英特尔处理器32位<br><span class='p blue'>x86_64</span>:英特尔处理器64位<br><span class='p gray'>ips</span>:苹果应用</p></div><h1 id="安卓"><a href="#安卓" class="headerlink" title="安卓"></a>安卓</h1><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/fcitx5-android/fcitx5-android/releases"   title="输入法：fcitx5"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>输入法：fcitx5</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/FossifyOrg/Gallery/releases"   title="相册：图库"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>相册：图库</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/octoshrimpy/quik/releases"   title="短信：QUIK"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>短信：QUIK</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/JunkFood02/Seal/releases"   title="流媒体下载器：Seal"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>流媒体下载器：Seal</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/TachibanaGeneralLaboratories/download-navi/releases"   title="下载器：Download Navi"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>下载器：Download Navi</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/TachibanaGeneralLaboratories/download-navi/releases"   title="文件管理器：质感文件"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>文件管理器：质感文件</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/breezy-weather/breezy-weather/releases"   title="天气：Breezy Weather"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>天气：Breezy Weather</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/thunderbird/thunderbird-android/releases"   title="邮箱：K-9"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>邮箱：K-9</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/jd1378/otphelper/releases"   title="验证码自动复制器：OtpHelpel"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>验证码自动复制器：OtpHelpel</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/orz12/pilipala/release"   title="bilibili客户端：PilipalaX"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>bilibili客户端：PilipalaX</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/Droid-ify/client/releases"   title="F-Droid:Droid-ify"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>F-Droid:Droid-ify</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/xiaoyaocz/dart_simple_live/releases"   title="直播客户端：Simple Live"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>直播客户端：Simple Live</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://f-droid.org/packages/de.danoeh.antennapod/"   title="播客：AntennaPod"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>播客：AntennaPod</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/spacecowboy/Feeder/releases"   title="RSS阅读：Feeder"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>RSS阅读：Feeder</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/foobnix/LibreraReader/releases"   title="阅读工具：Librera FD"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>阅读工具：Librera FD</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/Kunzisoft/KeePassDX/releases"   title="密码管理器：KeePassDX"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>密码管理器：KeePassDX</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/localsend/localsend/releases"   title="局域网数据传输：LocalSend"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>局域网数据传输：LocalSend</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/Futsch1/medTimer/releases"   title="吃药提醒：medTimer"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>吃药提醒：medTimer</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://f-droid.org/packages/com.drip/"   title="月经生理跟踪：Drip"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>月经生理跟踪：Drip</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/NobodyForNothing/blood-pressure-monitor-fl/releases"   title="血压记录Blood pressure monitor"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>血压记录Blood pressure monitor</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://viayoo.com/zh-cn/"   title="浏览器 ：Via"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>浏览器 ：Via</span></a><h1 id="Windwos"><a href="#Windwos" class="headerlink" title="Windwos"></a>Windwos</h1><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://keepass.info/download.html"   title="密码管理器：KeePass Password"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>密码管理器：KeePass Password</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://7-zip.org/"   title="压缩工具：7-Zip"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>压缩工具：7-Zip</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/xiaoyaocz/dart_simple_live/releases"   title="看直播：Simple Live"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>看直播：Simple Live</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://github.com/localsend/localsend/releases"   title="局域网数据传输：LocalSend"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>局域网数据传输：LocalSend</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu green larger" href="https://www.thunderbird.net/zh-CN/"   title="邮箱客户端：：Thunderbird"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>邮箱客户端：：Thunderbird</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://geekuninstaller.com/"   title="卸载工具：Geek"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>卸载工具：Geek</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://www.internetdownloadmanager.com/"   title="下载器：IDM"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>下载器：IDM</span></a><a class="btn-anzhiyu orange larger" href="https://www.voidtools.com/zh-cn/"   title="搜索文件：everything"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-circle-arrow-right"></i><span>搜索文件：everything</span></a>]]></content>
      
      
